1. Select word

    Success

        1) Word selection from dropdown menu:
            - "ab" characters typing
            - dropdown menu has shown
            - select a word in a dropdown menu
            - wordAutoCompleteTextView shows selected word

        2) Manual word typing, - word not found in a database dictionary:
            - "yqzyqz" characters typing
            - click 'ok' button
            - wordAutoCompleteTextView shows confirmed word

    Error

        1) Database error on word typing
            - type "ab" characters
            - database error is thrown
            - show a message: "database error, type a word manually, please"


2. Select translation

    Success

        1) Select a translation in list extracted from database
            - click translationSpinner
            - click on the item in a dropdown menu
            - clicked item is in the translationSpinner

    Error

        2) Database error on attempt to select translation from dropDownMenu
            - click translationSpinner
            - database error is thrown
            - show a message: "database error, type a translation manually, please"


3. Select example

    Success
        1) Select an example pair(sentence - translation) in a list extracted from database
            - click exampleSpinner
            - click on the item in a dropdown menu
            - clicked item is in the exampleSpinner

    Error
        1) Database error on attempt to select an example pair(sentence - translation)
            in a list extracted from database

                - click exampleSpinner
                - database error is thrown
                - show a message: "database error, type an example manually, please"

4. Select image

    Success

        1) Select image in a imageSpinner filled by image Api

            - click imageSpinner
            - click the image in a dropdown menu
            - selected image in a collapsed imageSpinner

    Error

        1) NoConnectivityException is thrown on an imageSpinner click:

             - turn off internet
             - click imageSpinner
             - show a message: "check your network connection to load an image"
             - enable internet
             - imageSpinner loads without extra click on it
             - network error message dismiss

        2) Network connection timeout has expired:

            - turn off internet
            - click imageSpinner
            - show a message: "check your network connection to load an image"
            - wait for 30 seconds
            - dismiss `network connection check message`
            - show a dialog:
                    "no internet connection:
                            - skip image selection
                            - download the image from gallery"

        3) server ConnectException

            - click imageSpinner
            - server connection exception is thrown
            - show a dialog: "image source connection error:
                                    - skip image selection
                                    - download from gallery"

5. Select group title

    Success

        a. typing group is in a database and dropdown is shown, group is selected
                - type "fr"(`fruits` is supposed)
                - select a word in a dropdown menu
                - check: wordAutoCompleteTextView shows selected word

        b. typing group is not found, user types manually, clicks ok to confirm group name
                - type "fruits" characters
                - click ok button
                - wordGroupAutoCompleteTextView shows respective group name


    Error
        a. In a moment of group typing a database error is thrown,
            - type "fr" characters
            - show a message: "database error: type a group manually"


6. CreateButton click

    Success

        1. createButton click appends new card to cardGroupFragment
            - click create button
            - cardGroupFragment inflation
            - check new card presence

    Error
        1. Error inflating class fragment
            - click create button
            - show a message: "Error: card group list could not be shown"

7. Skip image selection

    - click skipImage button
    - imageSpinner replaced with noImageTextView
    - focus gained by cardGroupAutoCompleteTextView

8. Download image from gallery
    - click downloadImageFromGalleryButton
    - select image from spinner
    - selected image in a collapsed imageSpinner